- Use the telegraf package for working with Telegram API
- Support two operational modes: long polling for local development and webhook for deployment
- Use emojis sparingly to enhance readability without being excessive
- For long multi-step operations
    - Display temporary status messages (e.g., "Getting information from OpenAI...")
    - Remove these temporary messages once the step completes to keep the chat clean
- When possible, update a single message progressively rather than sending multiple messages as each step completes